From 0b9ecc606a9b94b0306c5b3d4f29498ca419751d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2026 06:55:09 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] gst-plugins: drop using imported include dirs

Using include dirs imported from other non-installed IMSDK plugins
result in include path being poisoned with /usr/include/gstreamer-1.0.
Drop those from the include path.

Upstream-Status: Submitted [https://github.com/qualcomm/gst-plugins-imsdk/pull/8]
Signed-off-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@oss.qualcomm.com>
